[H5N1 outbreaks involving poultry and wild birds in Hong Kong have been occurring since December 2012. The outbreak goes on, but poultry has not been affected for a while. Both species reported here have been found dead from H5N1 in the past. Confirmatory tests are pending.

A Healthmap/ProMED-mail map of Shek Kip Mei can be found at: http://healthmap.org/r/1*XH. - Mod.PMB]
